Plot: Director Timothy Greenfield-Sanders spotlights 15 women who define contemporary American culture; included are Madeleine Albright, Margaret Cho, Edie Falco, Betsey Johnson, Alicia Keys, Nancy Pelosi, Rosie Perez and Wendy Williams.
Title: The Women's List
Actors: Madeleine Albright, Gloria Allred, Laurie Anderson, Sara Blakely
